---
# Rename this file to "amount-by-status.md" to activate.
# Documentation: https://docs.cube.dev/admin/ai/certified-queries

description: "Total order amount grouped by status"
user_request: "Show me total amount by order status"
---
SELECT
  status,
  MEASURE(amount) AS total_amount
FROM orders
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY 2 DESC
